{"tid":2079401,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"有冇人睇好藤井風同Vaundy","createTime":"2020-06-25T19:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T17:09:46.000Z","uid":200713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"06a77c15ba5cd56e7145ce5b170797d3f1f47b3e","tid":2079401,"uid":200713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T19:09:31.000Z","msg":"藤井風同Vaundy我個人覺得今年一定會紅起<br />\n<br />\n講講藤井風先<br />\n以前俾老豆叫嚟緊係YouTube嘅時代<br />\n拍埋唔同嘅cover片etc 夾埋3000萬views<br />\n到近期major debut album直上日本billboard第一<br />\n佢Live時會講埋英文雖然仲有少少日本口音但絕對易明過一般日式英文<br />\n第一隻歌何なんw<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nt6ZwuVzOS4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNt6ZwuVzOS4&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SkwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=1aa46395\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nt6ZwuVzOS4</a><br />\n<br />\nFull album<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_nuS1IYhaVBgIgRC4wti3aWxjOqwZo4NyA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DOLAK5uy_nuS1IYhaVBgIgRC4wti3aWxjOqwZo4NyA&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SkwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=a757c9b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_nuS1IYhaVBgIgRC4wti3aWxjOqwZo4NyA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到Vaundy<br />\n00後00年出世 個人覺得幾有風格嘅肥仔<br />\n初初識係東京flash<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SIuF37EWaLU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSIuF37EWaLU&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SkwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=dad29508\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SIuF37EWaLU</a><br />\n之後再搵埋佢其他歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Gbz2C2gQREI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGbz2C2gQREI&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SkwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=639a1585\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Gbz2C2gQREI</a><br />\n發現佢好多唔同風格嘅歌 <br />\n佢自己都話冇特別定行邊種路線<br />\n想作咩就作咩<br />\n個人幾睇好佢<br />\n佢同藤井風差唔多時期出album<br />\nalbum入面最鍾意<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZeIGVnkYX04\" data-sr-url=\"https://